"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.20.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.20.1</span> 標題：鋪道、石板地、鋪石地、鋪華石處（pavement, The Pavement）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： לְבֵנָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lvenah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:10\">EXO 24:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַלְבֵּן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： malben)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:9\">JER 43:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： רִצְפָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ritsfah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:3\">2CH 7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:17\">EZK 40:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:17\">EZK 40:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:18\">EZK 40:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:18\">EZK 40:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek42:3\">EZK 42:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： λιθόστρωτον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lithostrōton)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:13\">JHN 19:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἔδαφος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： edafos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir11:5\">SIR 11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir20:18\">SIR 20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:19\">BEL 1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc2:22\">3MA 2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc6:7\">4MA 6:7</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0437_pavement_roman_petra.jpg\" alt=\"羅馬人行道，佩特拉（Petra）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">羅馬人行道，佩特拉（Petra） (© High Contrast, CC BY 3.0 DE, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>石板地是用扁平的石塊鋪成的一個區域，該區域形成一個庭院（而不是道路）。「鋪華石處」是羅馬人的安東尼亞堡內庭院的名稱，該堡與耶路撒冷聖殿建築群的西北角相接。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:9\">JER 43:9</a> ：希伯來文<em>malben</em> 出現在其他地方時，意為「磚模」或「磚窰」（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.8.1 磚模、磚窰 (brick mold, brickkiln)&lt;REALIA:1.8.1&gt;</a> 中的討論及經文出處）。在這節經文中，該詞似乎是指鋪地的材料；許多譯本都將這個詞譯為「鋪磚路面」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）。上帝吩咐耶利米把石頭藏在「<em>malben</em> 的<em>melet</em> 中」。希伯來文<em>melet</em> 只出現在此處，意思不確定。各譯本通常把它譯為鋪設磚塊時用到的某種材料，例如「黏土」（“clay”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ）、「砂漿」（“mortar”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）或「水泥」（“cement”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> ）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 避免使用特定材料的名稱，而是著重於位置，英文意為「在鋪磚路面下面」。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:13\">JHN 19:13</a> ：在一些語言中，翻譯者可以把「鋪華石處」譯為：「用大塊扁平石頭鋪成的院子」，或「鋪著石頭的院子」。</p>\n<p>希臘文<em>edafos</em> 並不是指某個特定的地方，甚至不是指某種特殊的建築。因此，翻譯者可以使用一個統稱，例如「地板」，甚至是「地面」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
